==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: yī zhī cǎo, yī diǎn lù
===[[Min Nan]]===
[[POJ]]: chi̍t-ki-chháu, chi̍t-tiám-lō·

===Etymology===
Literally: For every blade of grass, there is a drop of dew.

===Proverb===
'''[[一]][[枝]][[草]]，[[一]][[点]][[露]]'''

# As long as one is still breathing, one has a chance to live.
# There is always a way out.

===Alternate forms===
[[一枝草，一點露]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

